trans-unit.source: Represents a polygon annotation.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en polygon merknad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Henter merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: For internal use, should not be used.
trans-unit.target: For intern bruk, kan ikke brukes.

trans-unit.source: The annotation type.
trans-unit.target: Merknadstypen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background color of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background gradient style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsstilen gradering for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the gradient fill; the primary color is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A> property and the secondary color is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne gradering Fyll; den primære fargen er angitt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>egenskapen og den sekundære fargen er angitt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.GradientStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background hatch style of an annotation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir skraveringsstilen for merknadsbakgrunnen for en merknad.

trans-unit.source: Two colors are used to draw the hatching fill; the primary color is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A> property and the secondary color is specified with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: To farger brukes til å tegne skravering Fyll; den primære fargen er angitt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>egenskapen og den sekundære fargen er angitt med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackSecondaryColor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartHatchStyle"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne bakgrunnsfargen for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the secondary color of the annotation background.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den sekundære fargen for bakgrunn for merknaden.

trans-unit.source: This secondary color is used with a primary color, defined with the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A> property, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A> properties are used.
trans-unit.target: Denne sekundære fargen brukes med en primær farge definert med den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>egenskapen, da den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A>Egenskaper brukes.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackGradientStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackHatchStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.PolygonAnnotation.BackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> value used to draw the annotation background with hatching or gradient fill.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"> </xref> verdien brukes til å tegne merknadsbakgrunnen skravering eller gradering fyll.
